msgstr "Caawin"

#: app/templates/help.html:7
msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli wuxuu leeyahay tilmaamo dhex-dhexaad ah oo kuu saamaxaya inaad "
"habayso oo maamusho qaabeyntaada."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Boggan wuxuu bixiyaa dulmar guud oo ah astaamaha muhiimka ah iyo xiriirada "
"tooska ah ee laga maamuli karo."

